REGRESSION
========================================================
id: regression
type: prompt


```{r}
out <- lm(Amount ~ Freq24+Dollar24,data=Clothing)
library(knitr)
kable(summary(out)$coef, digits=2)
```


this is the equation $$y_i=\beta_1*x_1+beta_2*x_2 $$


